content.html: Anya Taylor-Joy says that she can't drive despite playing Furiosa in the upcoming 'Mad Max' prequel: “I don’t actually have a license. I can’t go on a highway, I can’t parallel park, but if you need me to do a juicy 180 in a truck, I can do that and not hit the camera people.”
content.value:
Anya Taylor-Joy says that she can't drive despite playing Furiosa in the upcoming 'Mad Max' prequel:

“I don’t actually have a license. I can’t go on a highway, I can’t parallel park, but if you need me to do a juicy 180 in a truck, I can do that and not hit the camera people.”
